title: Content OCE.....
body: So I'm wondering why we don't have any features yet for OCE its becoming quite boring and most people I talk to want to transfer back to NA just to get content such as DOMINION like I don't see how we can't have nice things its not like there's any wait times longer then 3 mins for anything but team builder. So finishing up, are the players in oce just not worth their time? or are they neglecting us like a bad child that's in the naughty corner for something it didn't do?

replies.body:
Most people you talk to would sacrifice 100ping permanently to play Dominion?

I don't think I value those peoples opinion. :D
Especially when you can still set up customs. Just no queue.
We don't have a large enough population actually.
